    <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/50 p-4 mb-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium mb-2">🎓 Why This Helps You Win at Scrabble</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Competitive Scrabble players don't just know words — they've <strong class="text-white">memorised</strong> thousands of obscure but legal words and can recall them instantly under pressure. The Activities system mimics how top players train: daily exposure to new words (WOTD), timed recall under pressure (Quiz), and repetitive review (Memory WordBench). Research in cognitive science shows that <strong class="text-white">active recall + spaced repetition</strong> is 3–5× more effective than passive reading for long-term memory. Use these tools for just 5 minutes a day and you'll notice words coming to you faster during real games.</p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-400 mt-6 mb-3">📖 Word of the Day</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Every day a new Scrabble-worthy word is featured with its meaning and fun facts. The goal is simple: learn one new word per day, and within a month you'll have 30 new weapons in your arsenal.</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>A fresh word appears automatically each day — no action needed from you</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Click <strong class="text-white">📖 Lookup</strong> to fetch the full dictionary definition instantly</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Click <strong class="text-white">+ Add to Memory WordBench</strong> to save it to your personal word bank for later review</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Words are cached for 24 hours — loads instantly even offline after first visit</span></li>
