    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">A timed vocabulary challenge that tests your word knowledge under pressure — just like a real game where the clock is ticking.</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span><strong class="text-white">Pick your challenge level:</strong> Choose 3, 5, 7, or 10 words per round</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span><strong class="text-white">Set your timer:</strong> From 30s (Expert) to 120s (Beginner) — find your sweet spot</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span><strong class="text-white">Match words to meanings:</strong> Pick the correct definition from 4 options</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span><strong class="text-white">Get real-time encouragement:</strong> After each answer, you'll see your score and time — keeping you motivated to push for a perfect run</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span><strong class="text-white">Track achievements:</strong> Every completed quiz is saved to your Achievements record with score, time, and splits</span></li>
    </ul>
