      <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium mb-2">🏅 Building Vocabulary Through Active Recall</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">The quiz uses active recall — the most effective memorisation technique. Instead of passively reading definitions, you're forced to retrieve the meaning from memory under time pressure. This strengthens recall pathways far more than re-reading ever could. Start with 3 words on Relaxed timer, then work up to 10 words on Expert as your vocabulary grows.</p>
    </div>

