    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Practice your saved words with a classic flip-card approach. Words from your Memory WordBench become interactive flash cards — tap to reveal the meaning, swipe to advance.</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 mb-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Cards are shuffled randomly each session for varied practice</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Colour-coded by source: purple (Word of the Day), blue (Quiz), amber (Saved), green (Solver)</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Navigate with arrow keys (← →) or tap Prev/Next buttons</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>Press Space or tap the card to flip and reveal the meaning</span></li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">→</span><span>The more words you save from the solver, WOTD, and quizzes, the richer your flash card deck becomes</span></li>
